data.description: Nestled in the heart of midtown Billings, this tastefully updated home provides many modern comforts including remodeled bathrooms and new carpet! Hardwood floors and built-ins complement the freshly painted bedrooms~3 on the main level~while a newly tiled kitchen backsplash & newer flooring along w/updated appliances grace the galley style kitchen. Downstairs you’ll find new paint in the spacious family room, stairwell & bedroom as well as updated recessed lighting. A large laundry room with sink, separate storage room & full bath round out the lower level of the home. An attached covered carport and two-car detached garage provide plenty of covered parking. Backyard is fully fenced with alley access making it a safe space for your pets. Within walking distance to nearby elementary school and close to downtown amenities. This home has so much to offer ~ go see it today!
